title: Scott Morrison - Wikipedia
snippet: He had a brief career as a child actor, appearing in several television commercials and small roles in local shows. Morrison attended Sydney Boys High School before going on to complete a Bachelor of Science (B.Sc.) honours degree in applied economic geography at the University of New South Wales.

title: Scott Morrison | Biography, Education, & Previous Offices | Britannica
snippet: During his childhood Morrison also acted in television commercials. He attended the prestigious Sydney Boys High before matriculating at the University of New South Wales, where he studied economics and geography.

title: Scott Morrison: before office | naa.gov.au
snippet: Scott John Morrison was born on 13 May 1968 in Sydney, New South Wales, to John Morrison, a policeman, and his wife Marion. He was educated at Sydney Boys High School, then attended the University of New South Wales, where he received an honours degree in applied economic geography.

title: Scott Morrison - EVP, Business Development at After | The Org
snippet: Scott Morrison has a BBA from the University of Miami Herbert Business School in marketing and advertising and an MBA from Widener University in marketing. Scott also attended Brandywine High School.

title: Why Scott Morrison sends his daughters to private school
snippet: "Students who are struggling in our schools, for whatever reason, need support and will continue to receive it in NSW public schools." Mr Morrison attended the public selective school Sydney Boys' High.
